      <section eId="sec_1399_TT">
        <num>1399-TT</num>
        <heading>Regulations</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_1399_TT__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>appropriate engineered sharps are not available in the market;\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1399_TT__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>the use of sharps without engineered sharps injury protections is\nessential to the performance of a specific medical procedure; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_1399_TT__subsec_c">
          <num>(c)</num>
          <content>
            <p>based on objective product evaluation, sharps with engineered\ninjury protections are not more effective in preventing exposure\nincidents than sharps without engineered injury protections.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
